reviews.review_text: Muddy The other audience recording is much clearer.

different strokes True, this one's on the muddy side of things.  The other recording is clearer, but on this one the band doesn't sound so far away (and with so much audience in between).  A toss up, but I'll probably also go with the other AUD.
Trippin' with Mr. Moore If you roll off the bottom to your preference, you'll be right there.  I don't know of any way to make a distant recording sound nearer.  This is Jerry Moore y'all.
